        "timestamp": "2020-07-13 04:29:01.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nThe toggle does something bit different; consider AaiController2.java:144:\n\n```\n        if (featureManager.isActive(Features.FLAG_FLASH_REDUCED_RESPONSE_CHANGEMG)){\n            return aaiClient.getVnfsByParamsForChangeManagement(globalCustomerId, serviceType, nfRole, cloudRegion).getT();\n        }\n```\n\nand the behaviour can be observed in AaiApiTest.java's tests and presets: getVnfDataByGlobalIdAndServiceType (flag is off) and getVnfsWithCustomQueryNewReducedResponse (flag is toggled on).\n\ngenerally it turns vid to use a different AAI custom-query -- vnfs-fromServiceInstance-filter instead of vnf-topology-fromServiceInstance -- to get similar vnf information, but with no vfmodules information.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
